    <string name="large_text">
        "The famous game of Beerpong is all about friendship, loyality and brotherhood.\n"
        "This app adds lots of shame, fun and challenges to it.\n"
        "The general rules of beerpong are taken for granted here, because this is basic knowledge.\n"
        "Darepong works as follows:\n\n"
        "Every time a team has to drink a beer, this team has the opportunity to make a dare instead"
        "of drinking the hit cup. For that, you have to press the cup and a dialog with the dare"
        "pops up. If you did the dare correctly, you don't have to drink the beer, but if you don't"
        "want to take the challenge or didn't complete the dare successfully, you have to drink the"
        "beer.\n"
        "But keep in mind, using a dare"
        "instead of drinking is possible only once per cup!\n\n"
        "Have fun!!"
    </string>
